{
  "sourceLanguage": "ja",
  "strings": {
    "": {},
    " ": {},
    " 提案": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": " Suggested"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "- %@": {},
    "·": {},
    "\"%@\" • %lld 件": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%1$@\" • %2$lld results"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "\"%1$@\" • %2$lld 件"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "“%@” の検索結果なし": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No results for “%@”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "“%@”から退出します。オーナーや他の参加者のデータは残ります。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You will leave “%@”. The owner's and other participants' data will remain."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "(無題)": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Untitled)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "(空の応答)": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Empty response)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」がこの端末から消えます。オーナーや他の参加者のデータは残ります。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“%@” will be removed from this device. The owner's and other participants' data will remain."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」から退出しますか?": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Leave “%@”?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」とこのシートのすべてのデータが完全に削除されます。共有している場合は参加者のデバイスからも削除されます。この操作は取り消すことはできません。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“%@” and all data in this sheet will be permanently deleted. If shared, it will also be removed from participants' devices. This action cannot be undone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」に %@ を追加しました": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Added %2$@ to “%1$@”"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "「%1$@」に %2$@ を追加しました"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」に参加しました": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Joined “%@”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」のパスワードロックを解除します。現在のパスワードを入力してから実行してください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Remove the password lock for “%@”. Enter the current password before proceeding."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」の支出について何でも聞いてください。\n例: 「今月の食費は?」「先週いちばん多く使った日は?」": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ask anything about spending in “%@”.\nE.g. “How much did I spend on food this month?” “Which day last week did I spend the most?”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を削除します。元に戻せません。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Delete “%@”. This cannot be undone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を削除しますか?": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Delete “%@”?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」を開く": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open “%@”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「コーヒー 350 円」と話しかけるだけで支出を記録できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Just say “Coffee 350 yen” to record an expense."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「今月」表示時に進捗バーで残額を可視化します。0 のまま保存すると予算なし扱い。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Shows the remaining amount as a progress bar in the \"This Month\" view. Saving it as 0 means no budget."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「招待する」で登録した相手に、AirDrop やメッセージなどでこのリンクを送ることもできます。相手はリンクをタップして参加できます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can also send this link by AirDrop, Messages, etc. to people you added with \"Invite.\" They can join by tapping the link."
          }
        }
      }
    },
