            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Leave this sheet?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このシートとすべての支出が削除されます。元には戻せません。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This sheet and all its expenses will be deleted. This cannot be undone."
